#stance=stance1
#originalStanceText=Yes
#originalTopic=Debate:_Right_to_bear_arms_in_the_US
 "The people" should not be conflated to include only a collective right It is false and inconsistent to claim that "the people" somehow means only a collective, government-militia right. "The people" is consistently used in the Bill of Rights and Constitution to preface an individual right.
